WEBVTT

00:05.149 --> 00:06.930
Yes, the strangest thing
just happened to me.

00:06.965 --> 00:10.666
I had a conversation
with a neighbor.

00:10.701 --> 00:14.236
Wow. I never even saw
my neighbors in L.A.

00:14.271 --> 00:16.071
Except during earthquakes.

00:17.139 --> 00:18.984
Yeah, sometimes we'd pull
out of our driveways

00:19.019 --> 00:22.022
at the same time, and as our
electronic gates were opening,

00:22.057 --> 00:24.708
I'd think I don't even
know their names,

00:24.743 --> 00:26.370
and they don't know mine.

00:26.405 --> 00:28.461
And the world was good.

00:30.417 --> 00:32.327
Well, that was the L.A. us.

00:32.362 --> 00:33.577
Here in Cleveland,

00:33.612 --> 00:35.052
we're gonna get to
know our neighbors.

00:35.087 --> 00:36.901
In fact, I'm throwing
a party. Tomorrow.

00:36.936 --> 00:39.723
Look at me being
all spontaneous.

